 "summary": "In the massive bowl of the New Republic Senate Chambers in the Government Complex on Coruscant, a formal session of the Senate convenes, with the Sullustan Jedi ambassador Enb'Zik in attendance among the assembled delegates and Chief of State Leia Organa Solo. The proceedings address the pressing matters facing the Republic, the great stepped chamber filled with the weight of galactic governance. The log captures the formal rhythms and high-stakes deliberation of the Republic's central legislative body.",
